Summary: At 5:30 pm I was in my backyard and saw lights out of the corner of my eye and looked up in the sky to see a triangular craft with 8 yellow lights.
divs: Sighting Details1- Doing yard work in the backyard 2- lights distracted me 3- ufo, government aircraft 4- I never herd anything, it seemed pretty far. Looked like it was moving just like a jet would. 5- I felt very excited, and called a friend to see if he could see. 6- It traveled out of sight
